Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra. This is Jimmy. How can I help you?

Speaker 2: Yeah, my name is Louis Edmond.

Speaker 1: Mr. Edmond, before you go any further, you looked like you were transferred over,

Speaker 2: so can I get your phone number and I can probably fill up your account a lot faster that way, if you don't mind?

Speaker 1: Yeah, 931-367-4092.

Speaker 2: I took six, and they didn't do the same for me.

Speaker 1: Okay. I have your account up here, Louis.

Speaker 1: It looks like you're getting the Viagra, the 50 milligrams.

Speaker 2: It looks like they have you set up to get them every month by the doctor with your prescription.

Speaker 1: Is that too frequently for you?

Speaker 2: Because we can always postpone it and pause your prescription for a while, if that's what you want to do.

Speaker 1: I'll call you if I need some.

Speaker 2: Okay. All right. We'll put that on the pause for you. Not a problem.

Speaker 1: How much were those?

Speaker 2: You're getting a discounted price at $63.95, okay?

Speaker 1: Okay.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: All right. So we'll go ahead and take that. We'll go ahead and pause you out there, okay?

Speaker 2: All right. I'll stop sending no more.

Speaker 1: I got you. Not a problem.

Speaker 2: All right. Thanks.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
